description: A massive drone strike rattled Moscow and its suburbs overnight into Sunday, injuring several people. Meanwhile, a huge nighttime wave of Russian drones targeted Ukraine.
title: Drones Strike Moscow as Top U.K. Official Highlights Russian Casualties in Ukraine

description: King Charles III led the nation Sunday in a two-minute silence in remembrance of fallen service personnel in central London.
title: Kate Middleton Attends Remembrance Sunday Ceremony as She Slowly Returns to Duty

description: The first episode of “The Double Life of My Billionaire Husband” pans out like a daytime TV melodrama: a female protagonist asks her father and evil stepmother for $50,000 to pay for her mother’s kidney dialysis treatment. Cue an evil stepsister, who snarkily says that the payment is assured—if the lead marries the illegitimate son…
title: How ReelShort CEO Joey Jia Used a Chinese Trend to Disrupt the U.S. Entertainment Industry

description: The winner-take-all system breeds political disillusionment, turns voters off from democracy, and encourages extreme candidates.
title: How to Fix America’s Broken Electoral System
